text: Emily Maglio (born 13 November 1996 Cranbrook) is a Canadian female volleyball player. She was part of the Canada women's national volleyball team, and participated at the 2018 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship.
